name: Vasco
description:
Vasco, one of character in Webtoon - Lookism

Vasco is so determined to embrace his past. He's becoming stronger and stronger with his consistent dedication to protect the one he loves. Even though he is very clumsy but I love his honesty. This artwork is dedicated to all Vasco fans in this world.

It's for personal-use only. Please contact me if you want more of this artwork!
